thread.title: Hundreds join Cathriona White’s funeral procession
thread.title_full: Hundreds join Cathriona White’s funeral procession

author: NewsWire
title: Hundreds join Cathriona White’s funeral procession
text: 0 0 0 0 0 Dublin, Oct 10 (IANS) Supported by friends and family, the mother of Jim Carrey’s ex-girlfriend Cathriona White led hundreds of mourners through the streets of their hometown Cappawhite, Ireland as her daughter’s coffin made its final journey on Friday night. Some 200 people walked beside the White family as the coffin was removed from the funeral parlour to the parish church in preparation for Cathriona’s Requiem Mass, reports dailymail.co.uk Jim, 53, is believed to have arrived in Ireland and is expected to attend the funeral service in Cappawhite, Co Tipperary. The coffin was carried by members of Cathriona’s family, including her brother James, who served in the British Army and is a decorated Afghan war hero, from the funeral home to a waiting black hearse before it was taken to the church . The procession followed behind the coffin, led by Cathriona’s mother Brigid, stepmother Brid, brother James, sisters Lisa and Sarah, stepbrother Tadgh and her half-sister Larina. Cathriona, who took her own life at her Los Angeles home last month, will be buried alongside her father, Pat. Related Posts
